<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Détails du robot</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f3; color: #1a1a18; }
    .header { background: white; padding: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0ded8; }
    .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .logo-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; background: #185FA5; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .logo-icon img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; display: block; }
    .logo-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; }
    .logo-sub { font-size: 13px; color: #888780; }
    .nav { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .nav-btn { font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 14px; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 999px; background: #fff; color: #4b5563; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-btn.active { background: #0f3b7c; color: #fff; border-color: transparent; }
    .content { max-width: 720px; margin: 1.5rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem; }
    .card { background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15,23,42,0.08); }
    .hero { padding: 1.5rem 0; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #0f172a; }
    .hero-text { max-width: 720px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.7; }
    .title { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #0f172a; }
    .meta { color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .description { line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #334155; }
    .back { display: inline-block; padding: 0.9rem 1.3rem; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid #0f3b7c; text-decoration: none; color: #0f3b7c; transition: background-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease; }
    .back:hover { background: #dbeafe; color: #0f1f4a; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-icon">
        <img src="{{ url_for('template_logo') }}" alt="Logo RoboArchive" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="logo-title">RoboArchive</div>
        <div class="logo-sub">Archive FTC & ECAM</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="nav-btn {% if active_page == 'home' %}active{% endif %}">Tous les robots</a>
      <a href="/classements" class="nav-btn {% if active_page == 'classements' %}active{% endif %}">Classements</a>
      <a href="/forum" class="nav-btn {% if active_page == 'forum' %}active{% endif %}">Forum</a>
      <a href="/contacts" class="nav-btn {% if active_page == 'contacts' %}active{% endif %}">Contacts</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-title">Détails du robot</div>
      <div class="hero-text">Toutes les informations essentielles du robot, présentées de manière claire et rapide à lire.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="title">{{ robot.nom }}</div>
      <div class="meta">Année : {{ robot.annee }} · compétition : {{ robot.competition }}</div>
      <div class="description">{{ robot.description }}</div>
      <div class="description"><strong>Classement :</strong> {{ robot.classement }}e place</div>
      <a href="/" class="back">Retour à l'accueil</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
